These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, ivory
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who likes purple is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Color        | purple   | ivory   |
| Transport   | scooter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, trike
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Transport      | trike | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
1. the person playing poker is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Game          | scrabble | poker |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku |
| Pet    | dog    | fish |

 #################################

 
